  "title": "用 20%的工资去买 Token？旧金山开源大神：OpenAI 和 Anthropic 找到了 PMF！Anthropic 下场清理中间商，Cursor 倒逼开发模型",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODI5Njc2MA==&mid=2655940081&idx=1&sn=90f6d2cbe8d058dcd2313003706b3b8f",
  "date": "2026-05-28 16:39:00",
  "author": "51CTO技术栈",
